title: Front 242 1988 - Front by Front
description: This album is a pure classic in the EBM genre. It is also Front 242`s best release. This is claimed based upon both my personal opinion and what I believe is a widespread view. Includes the hits &quot;Headhunter&quot; and &quot;Welcome to Paradise&quot;, but also the manipulative &quot;Until Death&quot; as well as two versions of the experimental and underestimated &quot;Work 242&quot;. This album is the best start to F242 and captures the essence of the true 242-feeling. (Amazon)
